org.dspace.storage.rdbms

Class DatabaseLegacyReindexer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.storage.rdbms.DatabaseLegacyReindexer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.flywaydb.core.api.callback.FlywayCallback

    public class DatabaseLegacyReindexer
extends Object
implements org.flywaydb.core.api.callback.FlywayCallback
    This is a FlywayCallback class which automatically reindexes Database contents into your Legacy search/browse engine of choice. It is NOT needed for Solr, but is necessary for Lucene / RDBMS indexes.

    Reindexing is performed AFTER any database migration or repair. This ensures that your search/browse indexes are auto-updated post-upgrade.

    Author:
    Tim Donohue
